You've been searching for ways to get more Vis Discount out of your current gear, but solutions that rely on the tools you have are starting to become scarce. Nevertheless, with the addition of a Thaumatorium freeing you from the limits of your old Crucible, there's one more thing you can try.

These upgraded Goggles of Revealing... you're not sure what to make of them. They warp your perception, making you see or hear things that aren't there. Probably. But they also make challening Vis easier than regular Goggles of Revealing.

All told, you feel that is a fair trade. And having crafted this you'll always have it's power available to not just make it easier to craft better wands, but get more use out of them as well!
